{"tid":936624,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆成日係個廳食煙","createTime":"2018-12-11T02:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T08:26:17.000Z","uid":217822,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8443dfa546d5033994bec17cae6462f4ebfdfc25","tid":936624,"uid":217822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"由細到大都係咁。我地三姊弟氣管都有少少問題，佢次次食煙我地都好唔舒服，仲要真係好臭。佢叫佢入廚房食都唔肯，講埋曬的歪理話我剝奪佢樂趣。<br />\n由細吸二手煙吸到大。明明有做開運動，田徑跑中長跑有學界第一，但係肺活量都係中下，會唔會我個肺其實仲黑過啲煙鏟同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"94fa4a5b04eb28a42ecea0540e164ccad1cf704c","tid":936624,"uid":55924,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:12:54.000Z","msg":"買個牛角扇佢一食就對撚住佢吹"},{"pid":"a57bc5624e73c70fde7d7590e96c01ad9775197b","tid":936624,"uid":6244,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"你地氣管有問題佢都照食真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d33ba3646c488a328f954bf38818e4e2af01e2c9","tid":936624,"uid":43117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:16:10.000Z","msg":"佢係廳食煙就剪斷佢煙頭"},{"pid":"f5b21439685bc736d799b2a92e324422b2175718","tid":936624,"uid":16131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:16:30.000Z","msg":"試下唔俾家用"},{"pid":"a1244f3bf0711b9f052553430ad463883e32bf29","tid":936624,"uid":43117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5b21439685bc736d799b2a92e324422b2175718","tid":936624,"uid":16131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:16:30.000Z","msg":"試下唔俾家用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T02:17:22.000Z","msg":"唔駛試啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e5b82dd69208eab4948272cdba5042cde6f517","tid":936624,"uid":54481,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"reply